{"tid":1210974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得迪加與帝拿呢段好似我地呢加咁","createTime":"2019-06-12T14:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T17:08:50.000Z","uid":5737,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c08cbecb5332345d0630e69522d5a7e9610dd275","tid":1210974,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:49:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YCIcwuxHks4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYCIcwuxHks4&d=P3WkhlyCj4fBe8yrVMQ2y0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=70d5007a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YCIcwuxHks4</a><br />\n<br />\n50分鐘開始<br />\n轉在<br />\n請睇哂條片香港人都可以變成光，唔好放棄<br />\n條片都講得好岩，呢家每個90，00後都覺得可以贏，<br />\n所以依家唔可以放棄希望，無理由咩都唔做就結束<br />\n我地香港無超人，但人人都可以做光變成超人打敗怪獸<br />\n請分享 比失去希望既人<br />\n超人可能你覺得只係細路野，但入面同呢加情況完全一樣，唔好放棄希望"},{"pid":"28a4e06ab58bb7aa4505a0e5752cf1f0f3499492","tid":1210974,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:49:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e15c965fd8748af7fe8d645b501a22283e6ef213","tid":1210974,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:50:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6826c933bd88d973eec7f8e725298bee9cd668e","tid":1210974,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:50:57.000Z","msg":"香港人變成光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b95dd4742d01cbb6d763b816ff9fff065ecce4","tid":1210974,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:51:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2bb4bdfc264716228d56180e8f39d6c4f74aa6ee","tid":1210974,"uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"